# Menu definitions

DestroyFunc WindowMenu
AddToFunc	WindowMenu
+ I DestroyMenu Windows-Options
+ I AddToMenu   Windows-Options
+ I + $[w.name]" asd"	Title
+ I + "Here will be some options, later" Nop
+ I Schedule 1 Menu Windows-Options

DestroyMenu M=System
AddToMenu	M=System
+ "System Menu"			Title
+ "Reload &Config"		Read config
+ "&Restart Fvwm"		Restart
+ "&Cancel"				Nop
+ "&Fvwm Console"		FvwmConsole

